sentences: Scott Yanow (born October 4, 1954) is an American jazz reviewer, historian, and author.
Since 1975, he was a regular reviewer of many jazz styles and was the jazz editor for Record Review.
In September 2002, Yanow was interviewed on-camera by CNN about the Monterey Jazz Festival and wrote an in-depth biography on Dizzy Gillespie for AllMusic.com.
He also hosted a regular radio show (Jazz After Hours) for KCSN-FM, and worked as the jazz listings editor for the Los Angeles Times.
